// ================================================
// BASIC / CORE
// ================================================

Barrage - D-Rank
Requirements: None
Basic attack. Deals \~2 damage (1 base + 1 combo). No status effects.

Substitution Jutsu - D-Rank
Requirements: Ninjutsu D-Rank, Taijutsu D-Rank
Support. Gives user Substitution (1 turn, absorbs damage).

Healing Stance - D-Rank
Requirements: None
Support. Heals 1 HP (if below max) and applies Regen (2 turns, 1 HP per turn).

// ================================================
// WATER
// ================================================

Hydrate - C-Rank
Requirements: Water C-Rank
Support. Applies Regen (3 turns).
- If already Wet: +1 HP and +3 Wet duration
- If not Wet: +3 HP and Wet for 3 turns

Heavy Storm Jutsu - C-Rank
Requirements: Water C-Rank, Lightning C-Rank
Deals 2-3 lightning damage. Applies Wet for 3 turns (or +3 duration) to both user and target.
User gains Recovered for 1 turn.

Drowning Jutsu - B-Rank
Requirements: Water B-Rank
Deals 3 damage (+1 extra per remaining Wet turn on target). Adds/refreshes Wet for 3 turns on target.

Water Clone Jutsu - B-Rank
Requirements: Ninjutsu C-Rank, Water C-Rank
Support. Costs 4 HP (or removes Wet instead). Adds 2 Water Clones (max 3).
Clones perform barrage and apply Wet effects.

Kraken's Grasp - C-Rank
Requirements: Genjutsu C-Rank, Water C-Rank
Support. Applies Doom (5 turns) and Wet (3 turns or +3) to target.
Log: "becomes soaked in sweat and nerves"

// ================================================
// LIGHTNING
// ================================================

Static Field Jutsu - C-Rank
Requirements: Lightning C-Rank, Ninjutsu C-Rank
Deals 1-2 damage. Applies Numb (1 turn) to target and Recovered (2 turns) to user.

Chain Lightning - B-Rank
Requirements: Lightning B-Rank
Hits 4+ times for 1 damage each (ramp-up with Charged status on repeated use).

// ================================================
// FIRE
// ================================================

Fireball Jutsu - C-Rank
Requirements: Fire C-Rank, Ninjutsu C-Rank
Deals 2-4 damage + applies Burn (1 turn, 1 dmg) to target.

Flame Throw Jutsu - B-Rank
Requirements: Fire B-Rank
Deals 2-4 damage. Applies Burn to both target and user. Chains into Fireball.

// ================================================
// WIND
// ================================================

Razor Wind Jutsu - C-Rank
Requirements: Wind C-Rank
Reduces duration of all triggered statuses on target by 1. Deals 1-2 damage + applies Bleed (2 turns).

Wind Shuriken Jutsu - B-Rank
Requirements: Wind B-Rank
Skips TriggeredCheck. If target has Earth Dome: reduces it by 2. Otherwise deals 3-4 damage + Bleed.

// ================================================
// EARTH
// ================================================

Earth Dome Jutsu - C-Rank
Requirements: Earth C-Rank, Ninjutsu C-Rank
Support. Gives user Earth Dome (2 turns, blocks non-Genjutsu attacks).

Rock Smash Jutsu - B-Rank
Requirements: Earth B-Rank
Deals 5 damage.

// ================================================
// GENJUTSU
// ================================================

Demonic Vision - C-Rank
Requirements: Genjutsu C-Rank
Deals 1 damage + applies Doom (5 turns) to target.

Night Terror Jutsu - B-Rank
Requirements: Genjutsu B-Rank
Applies Numb (1 turn) + Doom (5 turns) to target.

Genjutsu Release - B-Rank
Requirements: Genjutsu B-Rank
Support. Removes Doom from user. Gives user Release + Recovered + Regen.

Hell Fire Jutsu - B-Rank
Requirements: Genjutsu B-Rank
Support. Applies Doom (5 turns) to target + Burn (2 dmg) if not blocked.

// ================================================
// BEAST
// ================================================

Bite - C-Rank
Requirements: Beast C-Rank
Deals 1 damage + Bleed (2 turns) to target. Heals user 1 HP if below max.

Summon Dog - C-Rank
Requirements: Beast C-Rank
Support. Costs 4 HP. Summons up to 2 Dogs (bite on your turn + absorption). Applies Bleed to self.

Bloodstream Barrage - C-Rank
Requirements: Beast C-Rank, Taijutsu C-Rank
Deals base + combo damage + applies Bleed twice to target.


